--- In EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com, Ursula Kalin &lt;kalinu@...&gt; wrote:
&gt;
&gt; Most people I know are in a group are not in it to be scared..Like you Adriana they looking for proof of some kind..I&#39;m a founder of a group..but I don&#39;t go ghost hunting..lol I don&#39;t have to,  I understand that some people are still looking for personal reasons or just being curious...I don&#39;t have my group paying for places we go..unless its like a very hot spot such as Mansfield which we are going in April but most places we go we are invited free of charge..we were just at a &quot;haunted hotel&quot; for free.
&gt; 
